verses.text: O \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* our \w Lord|strong="H0113"\w*, how \w excellent|strong="H0117"\w* \add is\add* thy \w name|strong="H8034"\w* in all the \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*! who hast \w set|strong="H5414"\w* thy \w glory|strong="H1935"\w* above the \w heavens|strong="H8064"\w*.

Out of the \w mouth|strong="H6310"\w* of \w babes|strong="H5768"\w* and \w sucklings|strong="H3243"\w* hast thou \w ordained|strong="H3245"\w* \w strength|strong="H5797"\w* because of thine \w enemies|strong="H6887"\w*, that thou mightest \w still|strong="H7673"\w* the \w enemy|strong="H0341"\w* and the \w avenger|strong="H5358"\w*.\f + \fr 8.2 \ft ordained: Heb. founded\f*

When I \w consider|strong="H7200"\w* thy \w heavens|strong="H8064"\w*, the \w work|strong="H4639"\w* of thy \w fingers|strong="H0676"\w*, the \w moon|strong="H3394"\w* and the \w stars|strong="H3556"\w*, which thou hast \w ordained|strong="H3559"\w*;
What is \w man|strong="H0582"\w*, that thou art \w mindful|strong="H2142"\w* of him? and the \w son|strong="H1121"\w* of \w man|strong="H0120"\w*, that thou \w visitest|strong="H6485"\w* him?

For thou hast made him a \w little|strong="H4592"\w* \w lower|strong="H2637"\w* than the \w angels|strong="H0430"\w*, and hast \w crowned|strong="H5849"\w* him with \w glory|strong="H3519"\w* and \w honour|strong="H1926"\w*.

Thou madest him to have \w dominion|strong="H4910"\w* over the \w works|strong="H4639"\w* of thy \w hands|strong="H3027"\w*; thou hast \w put|strong="H7896"\w* all \add things\add* under his \w feet|strong="H7272"\w*:
All \w sheep|strong="H6792"\w* and \w oxen|strong="H0504"\w*, yea, and the \w beasts|strong="H0929"\w* of the \w field|strong="H7704"\w*;\f + \fr 8.7 \ft Allâ€¦: Heb. Flocks and oxen all of them\f*

The \w fowl|strong="H6833"\w* of the \w air|strong="H8064"\w*, and the \w fish|strong="H1709"\w* of the \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*, \add and whatsoever\add* passeth \w through|strong="H5674"\w* the \w paths|strong="H0734"\w* of the \w seas|strong="H3220"\w*.
O \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* our \w Lord|strong="H0113"\w*, how \w excellent|strong="H0117"\w* \add is\add* thy \w name|strong="H8034"\w* in all the \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*!
